---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base>
    <article class="card onload-animation">
        <section class="onload-animation">
            <h1>
                Hi, I'm <em>Morax</em> :3
            </h1>
        </section>

        <section class="onload-animation">
            <p>
                a 22 y.o. college student majoring in Cybersecurity; born and
                residing in Iraq.
                <br />

                I'm just your average web dev who is comfortable building things
                with Javascript/Typescript & Golang, but I don't plan to remain
                as such.
                <br />

                I've been dabbling with C and systems programming recently. I'm
                starting to realize that programming <strong>IS</strong> fun, and
                that I'm simply exposed to the boring side of it.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="onload-animation">
            <h2>I welcome you to my humble abode</h2>
        </section>

        <section class="onload-animation">
            <p>
                I hope you like the theme switchers, it was a pain in the ass to
                make them look decent enough for my liking.
                <br /> Currently, I have nothing here except for these two movie reviews:
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/post/hackers-1995">Hackers (1995)</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/post/chainsaw-man-reze-arc"
                            >Chainsaw man: Reze arc</a
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="onload-animation">
            <p>
                When I have the time, I plan to have more posts that consist of
                ~80% tech post and the other 20% could be whatever.
            </p>
            <p>Anyway, enjoy your visit :3</p>
        </section>
    </article>
</Base>
